{"tid":1588484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【9.22太子站】蒙面黑衣女持伸縮警棍助清場　指揮官證：佢係警察","createTime":"2019-09-23T00:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T06:10:31.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"147373211a6a846b5e86ea7bc0f05186330a3d20","tid":1588484,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3317495/org/60b72bbf5feb45fd26a0831a0a042e73.jpg/dc30VdVEjz532n6vUY_L2owCswcXgRfkE5dluhOXZbo?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3317495%2Forg%2F60b72bbf5feb45fd26a0831a0a042e73.jpg%2Fdc30VdVEjz532n6vUY_L2owCswcXgRfkE5dluhOXZbo%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=62b4f52f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨（22日）網民發起機場「和你塞4.0」行動，由於警方重兵布防關係，臨時改為「全港性交通系統評估」，再度演變成多區「游擊戰」。入夜後，旺角警署一帶氣氛緊張，接近午夜防暴警衝出清場及制服多人。警員堆中，出現一名近似示威者衣著、手持伸縮警棍的黑衣女子，她沒有回答是否喬裝示威者捉人，但一名自稱「現場最高指揮官」的男警，則向記者稱「我話佢（該女子）係警察！」此外，亦有紥髻女子等數名男女，被質疑是喬裝示威者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3317480/org/6a71a79f88044dd53d47417bfff3f805.jpg/62Qnpw1QaDtNUMsncTWct0DieOrzV8UuQ6YLyEOmC8g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3317480%2Forg%2F6a71a79f88044dd53d47417bfff3f805.jpg%2F62Qnpw1QaDtNUMsncTWct0DieOrzV8UuQ6YLyEOmC8g&h=aa608667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3317481/org/0be8c964b6270c4501e0b8dce5a67d16.jpg/kZndf5txPQ4kBdblxqTSQ9IBYc3qHBDg1XwEJtV8BCY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3317481%2Forg%2F0be8c964b6270c4501e0b8dce5a67d16.jpg%2FkZndf5txPQ4kBdblxqTSQ9IBYc3qHBDg1XwEJtV8BCY&h=15b69631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3317483/org/0b21fadae5e47b2e0be3e5f993963657.jpg/sR7KirhOk3_Ni6B2_bKTQd7jfXvkn2cxzJiSw8yYksM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3317483%2Forg%2F0b21fadae5e47b2e0be3e5f993963657.jpg%2FsR7KirhOk3_Ni6B2_bKTQd7jfXvkn2cxzJiSw8yYksM&h=afebb452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3317482/org/6f3bc4058c0a1d7b3df2acd366c6fff0.jpg/07ISEI6LXIDFFtJt6yF8M8IN23rJdSpe8dqRk_HakZM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3317482%2Forg%2F6f3bc4058c0a1d7b3df2acd366c6fff0.jpg%2F07ISEI6LXIDFFtJt6yF8M8IN23rJdSpe8dqRk_HakZM&h=7d85c739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深夜11時許，大批防暴警員衝出，在彌敦道、西洋菜南街及弼街一帶清場，並制服多名人士。其中西洋菜南街近旺角道口，一名青年被截停，當時大批警員中，出現一名短髮、以黑色圍巾蒙面、身穿黑衣、手持伸縮警棍的女子，她隨隊繼續跑向西洋菜南街近弼街，該處正有一名青年被雙手用索帶反綁，按地制服。該女子趕抵後，與其他警員築起防線，當時其身上並無委任證或任何能識別警員身份的記認。<br />\n<br />\n在場記者見狀立即多次查問：「妳係咪喬裝示威者呀？拉人係咪要委任證？」她一直沒有回應，只不耐煩著在場記者「退後啲！」同時有一名男子向她稱「想行過去」，她更即時情緒失控，大叫：「你要行就行嗰邊啦！我做緊嘢呀，係咪呀？多得你哋唔少呀！」<br />\n<br />\n記者繼續追問該女子真正身份時，隨即有一名自稱是「現場最高指揮官」的男警，向記者表示「我話佢（該女子）係警察！」未幾她由多名警員護送下，登上警車離開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3317498/org/8a0cf6658e74e9ca4ad0837c2115a001.jpg/gfc5sEkb6so01IF9p5kEGCmRbP-ZPWAtCXhXfgl4V34\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3317498%2Forg%2F8a0cf6658e74e9ca4ad0837c2115a001.jpg%2Fgfc5sEkb6so01IF9p5kEGCmRbP-ZPWAtCXhXfgl4V34&h=9a66a876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方清場時，有數名男女被質疑喬裝示威者捉人，包括一名紥髻女子。（網上圖片/有線電視截圖）<br />\n<br />\n撰文：凌逸德<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/378110/9-22%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99-%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E5%A5%B3%E6%8C%81%E4%BC%B8%E7%B8%AE%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D%E5%8A%A9%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4-%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98%E8%AD%89-%E4%BD%A2%E4%BF%82%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F378110%2F9-22%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599-%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E4%25BF%2582%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=2f394c6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/378110/9-22%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99-%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E5%A5%B3%E6%8C%81%E4%BC%B8%E7%B8%AE%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D%E5%8A%A9%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4-%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98%E8%AD%89-%E4%BD%A2%E4%BF%82%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F</a>"},{"pid":"b0f3b27e93185123fc9338b39f0a789b5b0a5c65","tid":1588484,"uid":228589,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:01:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"841e5d148174638ad8b443d17f0f7bf1354b52d0","tid":1588484,"uid":3379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:01:47.000Z","msg":"達狗！"},{"pid":"2b879f6513646b1382410ff0ccbce6c11fa29185","tid":1588484,"uid":3379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b0f3b27e93185123fc9338b39f0a789b5b0a5c65","tid":1588484,"uid":228589,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:01:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:02:08.000Z","msg":"靚佢老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e43e012b77c6a40e0ff2ab9e5457558022e42cc","tid":1588484,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b0f3b27e93185123fc9338b39f0a789b5b0a5c65","tid":1588484,"uid":228589,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:01:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:06:29.000Z","msg":"人獸在香港是不合法的<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34dc328689af103a8c5900376949eff42bdec2eb","tid":1588484,"uid":85629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b0f3b27e93185123fc9338b39f0a789b5b0a5c65","tid":1588484,"uid":228589,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:01:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00: